{"tid":2315581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃張敬軒演會帶位員工確診，曾在5場演唱會入口分流觀眾","createTime":"2020-12-07T09:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T12:58:17.000Z","uid":50275,"like":26,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3db5742cd614559e5a52c57449a880bce839befb","tid":2315581,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T09:33:10.000Z","msg":"香港新冠疫情進入第四波，香港衞生署衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君在今日記者會上表示，截至今日凌晨，香港過去24小時新增78宗確診個案，有七宗是輸入個案，而71宗本地個案中，未找到感染源頭有29宗，而跳舞群組再多五宗個案，日出康城9期地盤群組已增至50人染疫，方樹泉宿舍再多一人中招。<br />\n<br />\n她特別提到，一名曾在張敬軒演唱兼職協助分流帶位的員工，亦已初步確診，曾於11月22、24、26、27及29日，在入口處分流觀眾入演唱會。並於12月3日開始發病，由於當時接觸很多觀眾，有機會有感染傳播鏈，加上演唱會人數多，每日有約6,000觀眾，八場有接近50,000人，「中間有傳播都唔出奇」，公眾若有不舒服、有擔心，應盡早檢測不要拖延。（編輯：陳詠恩）"},{"pid":"839672563eb2a1e2d082ea055a4ee3e6e0f149e3","tid":2315581,"uid":136797,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T09:34:19.000Z","msg":"多謝手足㩜炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9535fe4e83cd364b590a6c77624362ab57391a","tid":2315581,"uid":222581,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T09:34:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58c85f7e4c7e8225259416f73e909acf33f883a5","tid":2315581,"uid":50275,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T09:34:29.000Z","msg":"我認錯了，原來英皇軒仔好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6777b696a4abf0cc184aaeb56dd1832b99093922","tid":2315581,"uid":367090,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T09:34:46.000Z","msg":"電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317d28e46dfa7b64f2